articles.author: Rob Picheta, Anna Chernova, Radina Gigova and Ivan Watson, CNN
articles.title: Emergency declared in Kazakhstan as fuel protests rage and government resigns - CNN
articles.description: Unrest broke out in cities across Kazakhstan on Wednesday, as thousands angrily protested a sharp fuel price hike that sparked the resignation of the Central Asian country's government.

articles.title: Kim Mi-soo, actress in Disney+ K-drama Snowdrop, dies aged 29, cutting short a promising career - AsiaOne
articles.description: A rising star in South Korean film and television productions, Kim Mi-soo, who appears alongside Jisoo of Blackpink in Snowdrop, died suddenly on January 5, her representatives said.
